                      Project 2 - Arithmetic operations
                      --------------------------------- 
  

Submitted Files
---------------
README - This file.

Add16.hdl       - Adds two 16-bit numbers
ALU.hdl         - Arithmetic and logic unit wiht 18 functions
FullAdder.hdl   - Adds 3 bits with carry
HalfAdder.hdl   - Adds 2 bits with carry
Inc16.hdl       - Adds 1 to a 16-bit number
Mul.hdl         - Multiplies two 16-bit numbers
ShiftLeft.hdl   - Multiplies a 16-bit number with 2
ShiftRight.hdl  - Divides a 16-bit number by 2
Xor16.hdl       - 16-bit Xor gate



Remarks
-------
The Xor gate was made for internal use

to get rid of sign problems in mul.hdl,
I've multiplied the absolute values then put back the sign